          "rangeStart": 800,
          "rangeEnd": 833,
          "markText": "我们不能因为热爱而一叶障目，不能因为别人还不知道而心生嗔怒或轻视。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718759916,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-19 09:18:36",
          "chapterUid": 5,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=833",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=833"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_12_9785-9832",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "9785-9832",
      "markText": "艺术想占有人类的东西从来不是财富、权力和赞叹，而是时间，人类消费时间的总和才是艺术的价值所在。",
      "totalCount": 1936,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9785&rangeEnd=9832",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=9785&rangeEnd=9832"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_5_800-833",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "800-833",
      "markText": "我们不能因为热爱而一叶障目，不能因为别人还不知道而心生嗔怒或轻视。",
      "totalCount": 1586,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=833",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=833"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_23_7212-7233",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "7212-7233",
      "markText": "当然，没有鸡鸣，他也能按时起床，按季生长。",
      "totalCount": 1095,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7212&rangeEnd=7233",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=7212&rangeEnd=7233"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_5_2302-2367",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2302-2367",
      "markText": "因为我知道，如果它可以开口说话，一定不会炫耀辉煌的大唐，也不会怅然感叹耻辱的晚清。它会用温柔的目光抚过每一个来敦煌的人，语义悠长。",
      "totalCount": 1065,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2302&rangeEnd=2367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2302&rangeEnd=2367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_14_2774-2811",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2774-2811",
      "markText": "故事的好处是，只要人们讲的次数足够多、时间足够长，就会成为习以为常的共识。",
      "totalCount": 882,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2774&rangeEnd=2811",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2774&rangeEnd=2811"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_5_2056-2138",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2056-2138",
      "markText": "这是一个有趣的方法论，因为历史创造的最伟大的作品，就是一个个具体的人。怎样的历史就会塑造怎样的人，所以，如果你能仔细地审视自己，就能看到历史在你的血液里奔腾的样子。",
      "totalCount": 840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2056&rangeEnd=2138",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2056&rangeEnd=2138"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_12_10122-10198",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "10122-10198",
      "markText": "一个人变成什么样，取决于对自己时间的经营，古代百姓的时间和今天的打工人一样，大块时间被他人定义和支配。而当他来到石窟，他的时间就不再被生计和禁令所支配。",
      "totalCount": 781,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10122&rangeEnd=10198",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10122&rangeEnd=10198"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_21_3462-3556",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "3462-3556",
      "markText": "那些没有太多技法和套路的野生艺术，往往承载着一个小人物对当时世界最纯粹的理解，是敦煌历史最真实的面目。所以，我们不仅要看敦煌的大唐，看敦煌的盛大辉煌；也要看敦煌的晚清，看敦煌的孱弱与落寞。",
      "totalCount": 742,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3462&rangeEnd=3556",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=3462&rangeEnd=3556"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_18_9924-9986",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "9924-9986",
      "markText": "当一个地域内的所有人都围绕着一个文化符号开始想象和创作的时候，所有人也就身处在同一个精神世界里，这就是一个新民族的诞生过程。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9924&rangeEnd=9986",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9924&rangeEnd=9986"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_12_6577-6636",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6577-6636",
      "markText": "敦煌艺术最精美的部分，并不在如佛陀一样的大人物身上，而是在佛教世界的小人物身上，看敦煌，我们需要一双发现小人物的眼睛。",
      "totalCount": 708,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6577&rangeEnd=6636",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6577&rangeEnd=6636"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_22_8336-8420",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "8336-8420",
      "markText": "1956年，象牙佛收藏于甘肃省博物馆，1958年又被移交到今天的国家博物馆（原中国历史博物馆）。直至今日，象牙佛作为国家禁止出境文物，一直保存在国家博物馆的文物库房里。",
      "totalCount": 705,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8420",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=8336&rangeEnd=8420"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_12_10602-10655",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "10602-10655",
      "markText": "这么看来，石窟就像浪矢先生的解忧杂货店，关上门，一片漆黑，没有时间的流逝，你只需要静静等待，墙壁上的来信。",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10602&rangeEnd=10655",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=10602&rangeEnd=10655"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_7_1657-1692",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1657-1692",
      "markText": "当一车车的美玉从敦煌输送到中原的时候，它们经过的第一个关口就叫玉门关。",
      "totalCount": 682,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1692",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1692"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_4_420-509",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "420-509",
      "markText": "敦煌是文化宝库，是学术海洋；“敦煌学”是“显学”，也是冷门绝学。“为往圣继绝学”，是一份沉甸甸的责任和担子，需要的是甘坐冷板凳的清苦精神，也要有为历史负责任、敬畏历史的虔敬态度。",
      "totalCount": 666,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=420&rangeEnd=509",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=420&rangeEnd=509"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_13_7891-7955",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "7891-7955",
      "markText": "当屠龙少年变成恶龙之后，他最惧怕的就是有另外一个少年捡起他当年屠龙的宝剑。这也是资源的诅咒，你因什么而伟大，必然会因什么而消亡。",
      "totalCount": 650,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7891&rangeEnd=7955",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=7891&rangeEnd=7955"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_17_4849-4892",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "4849-4892",
      "markText": "曹议金通过几桩婚事，就解决了归义军的内忧外患，延续了归义军的生命。这是超高的政治智慧。",
      "totalCount": 648,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4849&rangeEnd=4892",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=4849&rangeEnd=4892"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_21_7033-7083",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "7033-7083",
      "markText": "至此，藏经洞的绝大部分文物都流失到了海外，陈寅恪先生因此发出了“敦煌者，吾国学术之伤心史也”的感慨。",
      "totalCount": 645,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7033&rangeEnd=7083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=7033&rangeEnd=7083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_20_3315-3381",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "3315-3381",
      "markText": "1528年，明朝封闭嘉峪关，完全放弃敦煌。自此之后的二百余年间，敦煌被吐鲁番或蒙古部落交替占据，陆上丝绸之路断绝，敦煌被中原人遗忘。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3315&rangeEnd=3381",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=3315&rangeEnd=3381"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_6_3811-3826",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3811-3826",
      "markText": "地理决定历史，历史层累出文化。",
      "totalCount": 598,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300041298&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3811&rangeEnd=3826",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/c4832a70813ab76a1g0188fb?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3811&rangeEnd=3826"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300041298_11_7561-7620",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7561-7620",
      "markText": "王粲下葬时，魏文帝曹丕亲临丧礼，并对同行的人说：“王粲喜欢驴叫，我们可以每人学一声送他。”于是在场的人就都学起了驴叫。",
